as="extraArgs"/></Field><Field name="command" currentValue="Function Get_Host_Info  {
    $os = Get-CimInstance Win32_OperatingSystem;
    $cpu = Get-CimInstance Win32_Processor;
    $system = Get-CimInstance Win32_ComputerSystem;
    $hash = [ordered]@{
        'os_version' = $os.Caption;
        'os_architecture' = $os.OSArchitecture;
        'system_drive' = $os.SystemDrive;
        'last_boot' = $os.LastBootUpTime.toString('yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.fff zzz');
        'install_date' = $os.InstallDate.toString('yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.fff zzz');
        'current_system_time' = (Get-Date).toString('yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.fff zzz');
        'computer_name' = $os.CSName;
        'number_of_processes' = $os.NumberOfProcesses;
        'domain' = $system.Domain;
        'manufacturer' = $system.Manufacturer;
        'model' = $system.Model;
        'system_type' = $system.SystemType;
        
    };
    $object = New-Object psobject -Property $hash;
    $up = ((Get-Date) - $os.LastBootUpTime);
    $object | Add-Member -NotePropertyName 'uptime' -NotePropertyValue $('{0} Day, {1} Hr, {2} Min, {3} Sec' -f $up.Days, $up.Hours, $up.Minutes, $up.Seconds);
    return ConvertTo-Json @($object);
};
